{
  "id": "adv_card_rei_10_01",
  "title": "一ノ瀬怜 1話 怜のジャングル探検",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――サニーピースが無人島ロケを終えて、数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Several days after Sunny Peace finished the deserted island shoot",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 1.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_01-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sigh…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.7999998251,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "顔色が冴えないが\n無人島ロケの疲れがまだ取れないのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You don't look well.\nAre you still tired from the deserted island shoot?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 11.5127435684
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_01-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "はい……\n無人島でのサバイバルは本当に過酷でしたから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes…\nThe survival on the deserted island was really harsh.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.3794102351,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "さくら達からも話は聞いているよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've heard about it from Sakura and the others too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.0127433935,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "無理をさせてしまったようで、すまなかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It seems I made you overdo it. I'm sorry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 24.2816093603
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_01-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "そんな、謝らないで下さい\nあの番組に参加したいと言ったのは私達ですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please don't apologize.\nWe were the ones who said we wanted to participate in that show.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.5482762019,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 31.4816093603
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_01-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "ただ、体力的にきつかったのはもちろんですが\nそれ以上に精神的な負担が大きかったので……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course it was physically tough‚ but\nthe mental burden was even greater…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.9482762019,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "無人島での不便な生活がそんなにストレスだったのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Was the inconvenient life on the deserted island that stressful?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.1482760269,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 40.1482760269
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_01-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "それもありますが、一番の原因は\n無人島にいる間、ずっと撮影されていたことです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That too‚ but the biggest cause was\nbeing filmed constantly while on the deserted island.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.4933747291,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 52.5267078875
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_01-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "カメラで常に見られていると思うと\n気が休まる暇がなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thinking that cameras were always watching us‚\nthere was no time to relax…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.4933747291,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そういうことか……。撮影されていると思うと\n番組を意識しない訳にはいかないよな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… When you think you're being filmed‚\nyou can't help but be conscious of the show.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 65.3301770049
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_01-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんです！　みんなカメラの前だと番組を意識して\n場を盛り上げようと張り切って大変だったんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Exactly! Everyone was conscious of the show in front of the cameras\nand worked hard to liven things up - it was terrible!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.8968438465,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_01-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "笑いを取ろうとして、ボケまくって、悪ノリして……\n大喜利大会を毎回止める私の身にもなって下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Trying to get laughs‚ being silly‚ getting carried away…\nPlease consider my position having to stop the comedy contest every time!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.4635105132,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 83.4968436716
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうか……\nちょっと俺の想像とは違うストレスだったな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I see…\nThat's a bit different from the stress I imagined.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "いろいろ苦労もあったみたいだが\n怜の奮闘は無駄じゃなかったぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It seems you had various struggles‚ but\nyour efforts weren't wasted‚ Rei.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "実は無人島の番組でお世話になったプロデューサーから\n怜に仕事のオファーがきているんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually‚ the producer we worked with on the deserted island show\nhas sent a job offer for you‚ Rei.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_01-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "サニピにではなく私個人にですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not for Sunny Peace‚ but for me personally?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.9853435036,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 99.9853435036
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "無人島で頑張る怜を見て\nこの子とまた一緒に仕事がしたいと思ったそうだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After seeing you work hard on the deserted island‚\nthey said they wanted to work with you again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 110.1969078537
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_01-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "そうですか……。私の頑張りをちゃんと見て\n評価してくれている人がいたんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… Someone was properly watching\nmy efforts and evaluating them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.9635746953,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 118.5969078537
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "仕事の内容は、アイドルが世界各地にある\n素晴らしい絶景を紹介するロケ番組で……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The job content is a location show where idols introduce\nwonderful scenic views from around the world…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.8020439143,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_01-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "やります！　そういう素敵なロケならぜひ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll do it! If it's such a wonderful location shoot‚ absolutely!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.7513033386,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 124.7513033386
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "今ここで決めなくてもいいんだぞ？\nもっと詳しい話を聞いてからでも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You don't have to decide right now‚ you know?\nYou could wait until hearing more details…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 133.3286316391
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_01-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "数あるアイドルの中から、私を指名してくれたんです\nその期待に応えない訳にはいきません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They chose me from among many idols.\nI can't fail to meet those expectations.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.5619651474,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_01-rei013.m4a",
      "text": "ぜひオファーを受ける方向で話を進めて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please proceed with accepting the offer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.5619649724,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 144.4619649724
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "それだけやる気があるなら大丈夫か……\n分かった、先方にはそう返事をしておくよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you're that motivated‚ then it should be fine…\nUnderstood‚ I'll give them that response.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 151.6987221554
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_01-rei014.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます\nどんな絶景が見られるのか、今からロケが楽しみです",
      "translations": {
